<HEADLINE>
FT  03 AUG 94 / People: Gestetner Holdings
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Nigel Palmer has been promoted to md and Neil Bunker to sales director of
NRG Group, part of GESTETNER HOLDINGS.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
