deregulation bill that is passing through parliament could change this.
Consequently, the CSO plans to introduce competitive tendering for part of
its business inquiries next year, and to extend it later. These inquiries
are currently conducted by more than 100 CSO staff at Newport, Gwent.
These changes would still leave the analysis of the data to the CSO.
